{"tid":560658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple公司的IT佬只是一隻被騎的Dog  前工程師解釋多Bugs原因","createTime":"2018-02-14T09:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T06:00:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9cef718e753366e016a834e77edc82224c9cb94b","tid":560658,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【史上最 bug】前蘋果工程師大吐苦水　解釋為何 iOS 11 經常出現 bug</span><br />\n<br />\niOS 11 自發佈開始出現大量問題，bug 蹤處處，用戶一度不情願升級 iPhone，結果傳聞蘋果會大幅改變 iOS 12 的開發工作，變成維護和改善 bug 為主，但是，究竟為何 iOS 會經常出現 bug？<br />\n<br />\n一個聲稱是前蘋果軟件工程師的網民 jarjoura 就在 Reddit 討論區大吐苦水，說 iOS 的 bug 是與制度有關，他認為項目經理騎劫了整個工作流程，苦了工程師，項目經理將不同的工作以編號排列優先次序，例如 P0、P1 是最緊急的，必需立即完成，P4 是不緊急的工作，可以放在一邊有空時工作。沒有編號而且沒有項目經理簽署的工作是不能做的，偏偏工程師每一日應付最多的工作，就是需要緊急修復的 P1。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/former-apple-engineer-said-why-ios-11-always-have-bug_01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fformer-apple-engineer-said-why-ios-11-always-have-bug_01.png&h=3fe0fc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就是因為項目優先次序制度，結果工程師們被迫為了所謂的 P1 終日奔波，每日都是「危機模式」，壓力過大，連假期也沒有心情過，如果工程師不會忙著解決所謂 P1，iOS 的 bug 會多得令團隊失望。至於 iOS 新功能，項目經理會將優先次序放到 P2，這代表基本上會延遲到 .1 版于才會推出，這是為何部分 iOS 的新功能例如 iOS 8.1 的 Apple Pay、iOS 10.1 的人像模式等等會延遲推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該工程師認為如果不改變<span style=\"color: red;\">項目經理騎劫工作流程的問題</span>，蘋果的軟件工程部分不會有什麼改變，工程師不能掌握發佈功能或修復軟件問題的自由，iOS 的 bug 仍然會湧現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/02/14/former-apple-engineer-said-why-ios-11-always-have-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2Fformer-apple-engineer-said-why-ios-11-always-have-bug%2F&d=2NT3ILbaMCQiFHNmecbQxjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=25b15973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/02/14/former-apple-engineer-said-why-ios-11-always-have-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"829a760ad3d21dc077e8266d61b71c297b83b816","tid":560658,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"iOS is great"},{"pid":"cd6dfca00e2e31eeb144fdbd6124b3d39c117cf6","tid":560658,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"829a760ad3d21dc077e8266d61b71c297b83b816","tid":560658,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"iOS is great"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d604d1ca8e44b06c181bca679e03b4ab0705575c","tid":560658,"uid":11719,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"個os寫得衰咪多bug，優先執bug有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3a8b7874d2ab60545270562338aadbabc3d794","tid":560658,"uid":25556,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n既然bug fix已經放p1咁優先<br />\nIt狗都日日跟緊<br />\n咁點解仲咁多bug"},{"pid":"69f3b4778ab3993452ff465646af0ebd43813693","tid":560658,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"pm管唔到流程邊個管？<br />\nbug唔清點加新function？"},{"pid":"a761579490eff3387908fb86702737e0066bd006","tid":560658,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"解釋多bug原因？<br />\n<br />\n解釋緊新功能延遅原因喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdca04e783395e37f32ec5892743bf3a1f44d5c","tid":560658,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim